                                <label class="custom-file-label" for="imageFileInput">Ch·ªçn file ·∫£nh...</label>
                            </div>
                            <small class="text-muted">Ch·∫•p nh·∫≠n file: JPG, JPEG, PNG, GIF, WEBP (t·ªëi ƒëa 5MB)</small>
